OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start but cloud
OL,6,Fwill gradually thin and break up
OL,7,Fthroughout the morning. Sunny spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping by the afternoon and in the
OL,9,Fsunshine it will feel mild for the
OL,10,Ftime of year.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloud continuing to thin
OL,13,Fthroughout the evening allowing some
OL,14,Flengthy clear spells to develop. Under
OL,15,Fthe clear spells some mist and fog
OL,16,Fpatches developing, especially towards
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
