OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FMist and fog clearing
OL,6,Fduring the morning allowing some good
OL,7,Fspells of sunshine to develop.
OL,8,FSunshine often hazy in the west with
OL,9,Fthicker cloud arriving here later.
OL,10,FFeeling very mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,13,Fmoving across the region on Thursday
OL,14,Fbefore turning drier and brighter on
OL,15,FFriday. Further rain likely later on
OL,16,FSaturday. Temperatures returning to
OL,17,Fnearer average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
